{
  "stem": "9777.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But beside that, with electricity and like that, we didn't observe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I finished four grade of elementary school in the Jewish school, and four grade of [NON-ENGLISH], means-- it's like a high school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I finished schooling, I was 14 years of age.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there were already bad times, and went to learn a trade in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The joint had, like, a-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] talent school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What you have a talent to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The trade-- you have to trace things and draw things and do things, copy things, what they were, you know, like on bulletin boards, to see what you have a talent to.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they decided that I could be a dressmaker, a milliner, or a flower maker.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, like silk flowers and things like that they used on garments.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother did-- insisted that I will become a dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't too happy with that job, but there was no question of any kind of higher education any further in those days.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was happening in Pecs with your non-Jewish neighbors and with the population?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I left Buda-- for Budapest in 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I haven't got any kind of bad feelings for any of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in a villa neighborhood, private homes, individual homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One side we had a very lovely neighbor, a youngish couple.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He worked for the waterworks for the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were very, very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How I recall, after the war, my mother picked up a couple of things which one-- my grandmother gave it to them to hide.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was-- I corresponded with her for about two years' time, and she wrote to me about the hardships what they went through.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
